abstract: Rare flood in Missouri threatens hundreds of homes, causes sewage to pour into waterways and shuts down parts of two interstates.
lead_paragraph: A rare winter flood shut parts of two interstates, threatened hundreds of homes and caused sewage to flow into waterways.
